<span id="freeTextContainer10744874932719212763">What a brilliant piece of journalistic storytelling. I wish more such books depicting atrocities around the world get published. Honest, humble, amazingly well written and touches almost all the tenets of the brutal Sri Lankan civil war that went on for decades. It&apos;s a shame that one of the biggest wars in recent history was being fought so close to home yet I didn&apos;t know much about it. An essential read.</span>
