<span id="freeTextContainer2945977126725187100">A disturbing account of the stories , fights and travails of a populace caught between the totalitarian Lankan Army and the deluded , diabolical &amp; ruthless Tamil Tigers. <br/>Reads in part like a travelogue painting vivid pictures of the war-torn geography .<br/>The approach of this book recounting the war through the eyes and emotions of those who lived through it ( which is almost all the tamils) provides a more personal touch making it more engaging than other mere factual prosaic historical books.<br/><br/>If y</span>
  <span id="freeText2945977126725187100" style="display:none">A disturbing account of the stories , fights and travails of a populace caught between the totalitarian Lankan Army and the deluded , diabolical &amp; ruthless Tamil Tigers. <br />Reads in part like a travelogue painting vivid pictures of the war-torn geography .<br />The approach of this book recounting the war through the eyes and emotions of those who lived through it ( which is almost all the tamils) provides a more personal touch making it more engaging than other mere factual prosaic historical books.<br /><br />If you want to read about the Sri Lankan strife and are unsure about which book to pick up, this is definitely the one!</span>
